item.title: This is not a blog
item.description: It’s not a blog. It’s just a note sharing site. I created it because I have a habit of noting down everything, although most of the time I’m too lazy to compile them into articles. However, I think some of them is still worth sharing even in a very loose format. This is based on my years of experience of Googling. Sometimes, even several words in the search results may help.
